reviewText: Wonderful video for any child.  My son loves "fixing" things with his plastic tools and Handy Manny is just perfect.  It teaches them about working together to get things done and also working together with everyone in the community.

reviewText: Kids Love this. Great Stories and keeps them active.Much better than most of the TV shows out there.Keeps them entertained and actually teaches good stuff too.Recommend.
Title: Handy Manny - Fixing It Right

reviewText: Handy Manny: Fixing It Right is a 2008 Disney DVD compilation of five mini-sodes of the popular Disney Junior original series Handy Manny. In this DVD, Manny Garcia(Wilmer Valderrama, That 70's Show)and his team of magical talking tools travel around Sheetrock Hills helping out their neighbours by fixing and repairing everything. The DVD also has special features like a Spanish language track, and sneak peeks of other Disney favourites like Little Einsteins: Flight Of The Instrument Fairies, Johnny and The Sprites, My Friends Tigger and Pooh: Friendly Tails and Handy Manny: Manny's Pet Round Up. This Disney Junior DVD is perfect for anyone who likes to learn Spanish and helping learn how to work together!
summary: New Home Improvement Fun and Learning With Handy Manny!
Title: Handy Manny - Fixing It Right

reviewText: My two and a half year old found Handy Manny via the local library....borrowed it so many times I decided to order it. Fantastic Amazon price and shipping. Has several episodes and previews and two months later we are still watching it over and over!
